# My Solution

This is my implementation of the Angular test task.

## How to run
1. `npm install`
2. `set NODE_OPTIONS=--openssl-legacy-provider` (Windows)
3. `npm start`
4. Open http://localhost:4200/projects

## Implemented
- Lazy-loaded ProjectsModule
- GitHub repositories loading for user `sarccasm`
- AddUsername pipe
- Weather mock data added to page bottom
- has-access-token.guard protecting lazy module
- ErrorInterceptor handles 404
- Styles using BEM methodology


